Further updates to PSBT related code motivated by c-lightning usage.

This should be the last of the major interface changes although we might need some small tweaks when we get a second PSBT user.

@achow101 If you could review the final versions of include/wally_psbt.h and src/psbt.c that would be useful. Also the coverage report shows that finalize_p2pkh is never called, so we could use a test case for that added to src/data/psbt.json if you have one handy.
